    A Map containing the result of a HTTP/2 request and multi-response.
    Incubating Feature. Will be removed in a future release.

    This is one possible implementation of the aggregate result type <U> returned from HttpClient.sendAsync(HttpRequest,MultiProcessor). The map is indexed by HttpRequest and each value is a CompletableFuture< HttpResponse<V>>

    A MultiMapResult is obtained from an invocation such as the one shown below:

    CompletableFuture<MultiMapResult<V>> HttpClient.sendAsync(MultiProcessor.asMap(Function))
